  "title": "FAPO Turbo Headers for Chevy Chevelle Malibu El Camino A-body Small Block V8 El Camino Impala Bel Air Camaro Nova FE640150",
  "handle": "fe640150-fapo-turbo-headers-for-chevy-chevelle-malibu-el-camino-a-body-small-block-v8-el-camino-impala-bel-air-camaro-nova",
  "description": "<h4>Application</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Compatible with A-Body Chassis with turbo converted SBC 265, 283, 302, 305, 307, 327, 350, 400 small block Chevy V8 engines</li>\n  <li>Chevelle, Malibu, El Camino, Impala, Bel Air, Camaro, Nova, Monte Carlo</li>\n  <li>NOT direct fit. For turbo conversion only</li>\n  <li>Can be used for single or twin turbo builds</li>\n  <li>Up and forward facing</li>\n  <li>Does not fit 1982+ third gen Camaro</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Excellent quality and durability to improve vehicle performance</li>\n  <li>Shorty design for power gain from idle to mid-range RPM</li>\n  <li>Fully mandrel bent tubes made of high quality 16-gauge 304 stainless steel</li>\n  <li>Head flanges laser-cut from high quality 3/8-inch thick steel plates</li>\n  <li>The flange is flattened by a hydraulic press for precise and leak free sealing</li>\n  <li>All joints are golden color TIG brass style welded to prevent cracking and wear</li>\n  <li>Flanges chrome plated for corrosion resistance</li>\n  <li>Mandrel bent pipes to maintain free flow</li>\n  <li>The accessories in the photos are included</li>\n  <li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Technical Specifications</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<strong>Header Type:</strong> Turbo</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Primary Diameter:</strong> 1-3/4 in. (45mm)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Collector Diameter:</strong> 2-1/2 in. (64mm)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Head Flange Thickness:</strong> 3/8 in. (9.5mm)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Pipe Thickness:</strong> 16 gauge (1.5mm)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Material:</strong> 304 Stainless Steel</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Finish:</strong> Natural</li>\n</ul>\n",
